room_title: Escape room "Missing" by Skellington Manor in Bettendorf
room_description: Authorities have reported another missing woman in a string of strange disappearances. The Bi State Criminal Investigation Unit has selected your team to assist in finding the location of the missing girl before  time runs out. You will have 75 minutes to explore this multi room escape adventure game to find clues, discover keys and combinations to locked boxes, put all the info together to complete your quest before the clock runs out.
